{"tid":552276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 53歲雜工疑帶病上班　暈倒將軍澳地盤返魂乏術","createTime":"2018-02-06T11:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T00:16:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f19d9a5fcdbe4d9eac8f8856e8a771a7e83edf43","tid":552276,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:10:36.000Z","msg":"將軍澳環保大道與環澳路交界一個建築地盤，今早(6日)10時許，一名姓李(53歲)男工人被發現暈倒地上，叫喚沒有反應，工友慌忙報警求助。救護員接報趕至，將李由救護車送往將軍澳醫院搶救，惜最後返魂乏術。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，相信事件沒有可疑，惟死因有待驗屍確定。據了解，死者已婚，無兒無女，患有心臟病，在上址地盤做雜工，數日前曾向工友透露身體不適，感覺「沾寒沾凍」，至今晨出事前，他替電工用尼龍繩穿膠喉，之後到一旁休息，詎料突然暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180206/bkn-20180206120533079-0206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180206%2Fbkn-20180206120533079-0206_00822_001.html&d=mu2LrHILOiGtTxQfSHgwNFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=b163de48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180206/bkn-20180206120533079-0206_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"07b2fdf0af9f59f451f61b5d0500ad4a84485122","tid":552276,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"新樓咁快變兇宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6702c70b21b60f26e3d3efefc5e7d0a2ec8008ac","tid":552276,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"會唔會又係 專材？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9a7bb78e726168421c97354f40a02738313b0e","tid":552276,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f350b491df891870230ab11e135af5bbe37986bd","tid":552276,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42431125